{
  "name": "gcp-security-audit",
  "enabled": false,
  "transport": "stdio",
  "command": "uvx",
  "args": [
    "gcp-mcp-server@latest",
    "--read-only"
  ],
  "env": {
    "GCP_PROJECT": "${GCP_PROJECT}",
    "GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS": "${GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS}",
    "READ_OPERATIONS_ONLY": "true"
  },
  "notes": "DISABLED in MVP — rename to gcp.json, set enabled=true, CLOUD_PROVIDER=gcp, and connectors.cloud.live_write_enabled in autonomy-policy.yaml. Bind a read-only IAM role (Viewer or scoped auditor) to the service account."
}
